OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FITV News has uncovered further
OL,7,Fallegations of neglect of disabled
OL,8,Fadults at a major UK care company,
OL,9,Fwith at least one council placing the
OL,10,Fcompany under a form of special
OL,11,Fmeasures, as ITV News Investigations
OL,12,FEditor Daniel Hewitt reports.
OL,14,FAdditional reporting by Investigations
OL,15,FProducer Isabel Alderson-Blench
OL,17,FDisabled people and their families
OL,18,Fhave told ITV News that they fear
OL,19,Flives are being put at risk by one of
OL,20,Fthe UK's largest private care
OL,21,Fcompanies.
