OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation has found
OL,7,Fallegations of neglect across multiple
OL,8,Fresidential and supported living homes
OL,9,Frun by Lifeways, the UK's biggest
OL,10,Fprovider of complex care in the
OL,11,Fcommunity for people with learning
OL,12,Fdisabilities.
OL,14,FAfter our first report last month into
OL,15,Falleged failings at the company,
OL,16,FLifeways Chief Executive Andrea
OL,17,FKinkade told us that our findings were
OL,18,F"historic" and "rare".
