OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FNow, more than 80 people have come
OL,7,Fforward to ITV News with further
OL,8,Fallegations, including a mother whose
OL,9,Fblind, learning-disabled son, who
OL,10,Frequires one to one care, was left
OL,11,Falone when a fire alarm went off in
OL,12,Fhis flat.
OL,14,FAnother man with severe muscular
OL,15,Fdystrophy, who needs a ventilator to
OL,16,Fbreathe and carers to help him drink
OL,17,Fand go the bathroom, told ITV News he
OL,18,Fdeveloped a kidney infection, because
OL,19,Fno-one attended to him for two hours
OL,20,Fafter he repeatedly pressed his alarm
OL,21,Fto use the toilet.
