OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FITV News has now learned that,
OL,7,Ffollowing our first report, Lifeways
OL,8,Fhas been suspended from taking on new
OL,9,Freferrals by one London council.
OL,11,FMikey Simon has lived in residential
OL,12,Fcare for most of his adult life. The
OL,13,F47 year old is blind, autistic and has
OL,14,Flearning disabilities. He always needs
OL,15,Fa carer with him in the day, and two-
OL,16,Fhour checks throughout the night.
