OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FMikey's family installed cameras in
OL,7,Fhis flat in November 2022, telling ITV
OL,8,FNews they had become concerned that
OL,9,FMikey was not receiving the care he
OL,10,Fshould be. They say the cameras showed
OL,11,FMikey living a life of solitude; day
OL,12,Fafter day, he sits in an armchair in
OL,13,Fhis bedroom while his carers sit in
OL,14,Fthe living room.
OL,16,FSylvia says that before Mikey was
OL,17,Funder Lifeways care, he would be taken
OL,18,Fout into the community by his carers.
