OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,F"He used to be very active," Sylvia
OL,7,Ftells us. "He used to go shopping. In
OL,8,Fall the other care homes, as bad as
OL,9,Fthey've been, they've always allowed
OL,10,Fhim to come out into the community.
OL,11,FBut here, it just doesn't happen.
OL,13,FSylvia gestures to Mikey sitting in
OL,14,Fhis chair: "This - what you see here -
OL,15,Fis what it is. This is his life.
OL,17,F"They're slowly killing him. He's
OL,18,Flosing his mobility."
