OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FMikey requires two carers with him
OL,7,Fwhen he spends time outside of his
OL,8,Fflat, in the community.
OL,10,FIn 2023, the funding he received for
OL,11,Fthis was reduced, after the North
OL,12,FCentral London NHS Integrated Care
OL,13,FBoard ` who pay for Mikey's care `
OL,14,Fcould find "no evidence" that Lifeways
OL,15,Fwere providing the 35 hours a week of
OL,16,Fcommunity activity that they were
OL,17,Fbeing paid to.
OL,19,FIn November 2022 footage shows Mikey
OL,20,Fleft alone in his flat while a loud
OL,21,Fsmoke alarm goes off continuously.
