OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FMikey paces his room, clearly
OL,7,Fconfused, his mother says. One of his
OL,8,Fcarers enters the flat but goes
OL,9,Fstraight into the kitchen and does not
OL,10,Fcheck on Mikey - or reassure him that
OL,11,Fthere is no fire. A second carer then
OL,12,Fenters the flat, again ignoring Mikey.
OL,14,FShowing us the footage, Sylvia says:
OL,15,F"He doesn't know what's going on, and
OL,16,Fthey don't even comfort him."
