OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FIn January 2025, another clip shows
OL,7,FMikey going to the bathroom, where he
OL,8,Fcan be clearly heard retching
OL,9,Fviolently. His carers, who are sat in
OL,10,Fthe next room, do not check up on him.
OL,12,FIn April 2023, a neighbour of Mikey's
OL,13,F` another vulnerable resident who is
OL,14,Fnon-verbal ` can be seen alone in
OL,15,FMikey's flat at 10pm, helping himself
OL,16,Fto food from Mikey's fridge. Footage
OL,17,Fshows him in the flat for more than an
OL,18,Fhour, unaccompanied. Mikey is asleep
OL,19,Fin the next room.
