OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FThe building Mikey lives in has carers
OL,7,Fon-site 24 hours a day.
OL,9,F"My son has been in care for 24 years
OL,10,Fand this is by far the worst," Sylvia
OL,11,Ftells us.
OL,13,F"I actually think if it wasn't for
OL,14,Fthese cameras, Mikey would be dead."
OL,16,FMikey's care is estimated to cost
OL,17,Fbetween #3,500 and #6,000 per week.
OL,18,FSylvia says she is speaking out not
OL,19,Fonly for her son, but for other
OL,20,Fresidents as well.
