OL,6,FJenny Goodridge, acting Chief Nursing
OL,7,FOfficer for the North Central London
OL,8,FNHS Integrated Care Board, who pay for
OL,9,FMikey's care, said: "The quality and
OL,10,Fsafety of care is our highest priority.
OL,12,F"Since being made aware of concerns
OL,13,Ffew weeks ago, we have been working
OL,14,Fwith the council and other partners,
OL,15,Fincluding the Care Quality Commission,
OL,16,Fto make sure these concerns are being
OL,17,Faddressed as a matter of urgency."
