OL,6,FLifeways is one of the biggest
OL,7,Fproviders of residential and supported
OL,8,Fliving care for disabled adults in the
OL,9,FUK. Their 10,000 members of staff
OL,10,Fsupport more than 4,000 vulnerable
OL,11,Fadults with learning disabilities,
OL,12,Fautism, mental health problems,
OL,13,Facquired brain injuries and physical
OL,14,Fdisabilities across more than 100
OL,15,Flocations, as well as in their own
OL,16,Fhomes.
