OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FMost Lifeways contracts are publicly
OL,7,Ffunded, from NHS contracts or local
OL,8,Fauthorities. According to public
OL,9,Fprocurement analysts Tussell, Lifeways
OL,10,Fhas received almost #1.5 billion in
OL,11,Ftaxpayer money since 2016.
OL,13,FUnlike Mikey, 32-year-old Jonny
OL,14,FHowsley has the words to describe his
OL,15,Fexperience.
OL,17,FHe has been a resident at a supported
OL,18,Fliving block in Greater Manchester
OL,19,Fsince 2016. He has Duchenne, the most
OL,20,Faggressive and life-limiting form of
OL,21,Fmuscular dystrophy.
