OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FHe is physically disabled, relies on a
OL,7,Fventilator to breathe, and needs
OL,8,Fsupport with daily tasks including
OL,9,Feating and drinking, using the toilet
OL,10,Fand moving from his wheelchair.
OL,12,FHe relies on Lifeways to provide some
OL,13,Fof his care, including essential
OL,14,Fovernight staff, who he contacts via
OL,15,Fan intercom system when he needs to
OL,16,Fuse the toilet, or check his breathing
OL,17,Fequipment is working. The Lifeways
OL,18,Fcare that Jonny receives costs more
OL,19,Fthan #3,000 a month.
