OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FJonny tells ITV News he has been left
OL,7,Fbuzzing the intercom, sometimes for
OL,8,Fhours, with no carers responding to
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,FIn 2017, he says he was left needing
OL,12,Fthe toilet for two hours, resulting in
OL,13,Fa kidney infection and Jonny being
OL,14,Fhospitalised.
OL,16,FVideos recorded by Jonny last month
OL,17,Fshow him waiting on several occasions
OL,18,Ffor over 20 minutes for a carer to
OL,19,Fattend to him.
