OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,F"It does make it upsetting when you
OL,7,Fjust feel like no one is coming. I've
OL,8,Fbeen buzzing and buzzing and just
OL,9,Fnothing is happening," Jonny says.
OL,11,F"I don't want to degrade myself to
OL,12,Fwetting myself," he says. "Even though
OL,13,FI know I could resolve it and be
OL,14,Fcomfortable, I just don't feel like I
OL,15,Fcould cross that line to make myself
OL,16,Fdo that.
OL,18,F"It just makes you feel forgotten
OL,19,Fabout. Like my basic needs don't
OL,20,Freally matter.
