OL,6,F"It can make you feel a bit worried
OL,7,Fbecause if it was something major...if
OL,8,Fmy ventilator disconnects, I can
OL,9,Fmanage for about a minute, but I'd be
OL,10,Fgasping for air and in my mind I know
