OL,3,C'It's a life-or-death situation': new
OL,4,Callegations of neglect at care company
OL,6,FJonny suffered a broken hip in July
OL,7,F2022 as carers 'rolled' him from his
OL,8,Fwheelchair to his bed - a standard
OL,9,Fpart of his care.
OL,11,F"I just suddenly feel something give,
OL,12,Fand a loud crack. The noise just
OL,13,Frepeated in my head for ages," Jonny
OL,14,Fsays.
OL,16,F"I'm still on painkillers to this day
OL,17,Ffor it. The pain was a lot."
